1
00:01:32,479 --> 00:01:33,920
It's me, Zhixia.

2
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:38,440
Lu Jingxi!

3
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:39,280
Are you crazy?

4
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,000
Get out!

5
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,490
Are you still angry?

6
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,280
Are you mad about the banquet,

7
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:46,280
or that I couldn't keep my promise to take you away,

8
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,080
forcing you to marry my brother?

9
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,600
I've always wanted to explain it to you,

10
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,920
but he kept too close an eye on you.

11
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,120
I never had a chance to be alone with you.

12
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,600
I know you're disappointed,

13
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,320
but I want to tell you

14
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:06,090
that I've been dreaming about you lately.

15
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,360
I dreamt you told me

16
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,900
that as long as I took you away,

17
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:11,600
no matter where we went,

18
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:13,400
you'd be willing to stay with me.

19
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,520
Zhixia.

20
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,320
Lu Jingxi!

21
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,920
What nonsense are you talking about?

22
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,320
I am your sister-in-law.

23
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,490
Sister-in-law?

24
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,730
Even when he's not here,

25
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,000
you still want me to call you that?

26
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:27,760
Whether he's here or not,

27
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,320
I am still your sister-in-law.

28
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,079
Get out!

29
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,360
Get out!

30
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,320
Shen Zhixia.

31
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,970
What's with this chaste woman act?

32
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:43,320
When you were clinging to my brother

33
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,920
while dating me,

34
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:47,200
why didn't you tell me to get lost?

35
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,000
Wait a minute.

36
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,850
The smell is different.

37
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,200
Jingheng.

38
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,280
Something bad happened, Jingheng.

39
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:13,320
When I passed by my sister-in-law's bathroom just now,

40
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:15,320
I heard something break inside.

41
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:18,360
Then I called out at the door for a long time, but no one answered.

42
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,240
I'm worried

43
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,240
that she might have fallen inside.

44
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,740
Why don't you come and take a look with me?

45
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:26,960
Jingheng.

46
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,320
Cousin,

47
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:38,000
why are you in my sister-in-law's bathroom?

48
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,600
Just having a casual chat with my sister-in-law.

49
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,720
Who was chatting with you?

50
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:52,320
You were clearly the one...

51
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,250
Sister-in-law,

52
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,370
weren't we having a good chat just now?

53
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,400
It looked like you hadn't had enough.

54
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,800
How about we find a chance

55
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:01,560
to have a deeper chat?

56
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,370
What do you think, brother?

57
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:11,650
What do you have to talk about in the bathroom?

58
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,520
And look at you,

59
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,240
making such a big noise.

60
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:24,440
If others heard this,

61
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,040
they would think you two...

62
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:26,800
Cousin.

63
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,760
It seems that at the banquet before,

64
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,620
my demonstration wasn't enough.

65
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,120
Do you want to try?

66
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,960
Why are you glaring at me?

67
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,159
There's nothing between him and me.

68
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:40,880
We...

69
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,360
Listen to me.

70
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,520
This...

71
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:51,320
Let go of me!

72
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,600
Let go of me.

73
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,680
Let go.

74
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,360
Let me go!

75
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:58,760
Lu Jingheng,

76
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,720
are you losing your temper with me?

77
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,450
A man and a woman alone in a room.

78
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,880
He was soaking wet,

79
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,200
and your clothes were untidy.

80
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,520
Seeing such a scene,

81
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:07,920
shouldn't I get mad?

82
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,760
Or do you think this is perfectly normal?

83
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,130
What do you mean by that?

84
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,040
What do I mean?

85
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,280
Shen Zhixia.

86
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,000
How you and your greedy father

87
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:16,960
operate and cast your nets,

88
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:17,690
I don't care.

89
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:20,160
But since you've married into the Lu family now,

90
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,880
you are a member of the Lu family.

91
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:22,920
If you dare to let the Lu family's reputation

92
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,180
be slightly affected,

93
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,600
get out right now!

94
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:28,040
You think I care about your Lu family?

95
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,880
It was obviously your brother who broke in and harassed me.

96
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,240
You said I was indecent.

97
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,440
You don't believe me.

98
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:33,380
Let's divorce.

99
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:34,920
Let's divorce right now.

100
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:35,880
Divorce.

101
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,240
Fine.

102
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:39,320
But it's not your place to negotiate.

103
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:41,200
Call your damn father over.

104
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:42,480
Put the cooperation between the Shen and Lu families

105
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,140
on the table and make it clear.

106
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,520
When it is settled,

107
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,520
we will divorce.

108
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:04,280
I didn't expect Brother to care so much about Sister-in-law.

109
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,730
Stay away from Shen Zhixia.

110
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:11,120
As long as she is still my woman,

111
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,000
I won't allow you anywhere near her.

112
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:22,720
Didn't you despise her before?

113
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:24,940
What happened now?

114
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:27,500
Did you find out how good she is in bed,

115
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,240
or have you actually fallen for her?

116
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:35,320
This slap

117
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,960
is to teach you what you can do,

118
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,130
and who you can't mess with.

119
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,000
Also,

120
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,280
tell your annoying cousin

121
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,040
to stop playing

122
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,420
those boring tricks in the Lu family.

123
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,420
You want me to follow the Young Madam.

124
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,120
Especially her affairs before the marriage,

125
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:11,440
particularly her interactions with Lu Jingxi.

126
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,240
Yes.

127
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:16,920
If Shen Zhixia and Lu Jingxi really have a connection,

128
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:19,700
that would be a scandal for the Lu family.

129
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,660
We can't afford to take this risk.

130
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:29,160
Lu Jingxi made it sound so real.

131
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:33,520
Did the original host really have something going on with him?

132
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:37,720
Why would she ask Lu Jingxi to take her away?

133
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:56,200
What exactly did you go through?

134
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:54,320
This is the original owner's family's boxing gym.

135
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,800
She guided me here.

136
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,980
What was she trying to tell me?

137
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,120
Hello.

138
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,200
Why is everyone looking at me

139
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,880
like they've seen a ghost?

140
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:19,720
What a rare sight.

141
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:22,880
Usually Mr. Shen drags her here like a dead dog,

142
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:23,760
but today,

143
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:25,890
she actually delivered herself here.

144
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,560
The young lady probably

145
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:28,760
pissed off Mr. Shen again somewhere,

146
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,720
and ran over here

147
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:31,250
to get beaten and punished.

148
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,020
Young lady?

149
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,920
Have you ever seen a young lady

150
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:36,480
whose own father lets others use her as a punching bag?

151
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,560
I remember once,

152
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:38,720
you hit her in the ribs,

153
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,560
and it hurt her so much

154
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:41,640
that she curled up on the floor like a shrimp.

155
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:43,770
Her face was covered in snot and tears.

156
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,040
Mr. Shen even told you

157
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,120
to hit harder

158
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,640
to teach her a lesson.

159
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,200
You really are something.

160
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,060
Aren't you afraid of hurting her?

161
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,000
If she's hurt,

162
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,520
I'll just say I was careless in boxing

163
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:55,320
and lost control of my strength.

164
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,080
Get up.

165
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:49,520
Get up now.

166
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:56,040
I told you to get up!

167
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,640
Get up!

168
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:13,400
As long as I'm willing to take you away,

169
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:16,130
you're willing to be with me no matter where we go.

170
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:19,360
So

171
00:11:20,920 --> 00:11:23,280
this is how you survived in the past.

172
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:26,970
No wonder you asked Lu Jingxi to take you away.

173
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:30,160
Even if it's just a lifeline,

174
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:33,080
you'd try your best to grab it,

175
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,640
right?

176
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,400
You want to box, Miss.

177
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,160
You?

178
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,320
Are you sure you want me, Miss?

179
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,300
We're practicing boxing.

180
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,730
How can you not get hurt?

181
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:24,720
Jingheng,

182
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,400
what's wrong?

